{"id":24341,"date":"2025-05-20T07:00:08","date_gmt":"2025-05-20T14:00:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/?p=24341"},"modified":"2025-05-20T07:00:08","modified_gmt":"2025-05-20T14:00:08","slug":"glass","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.ronperrier.net\/2025\/05\/20\/glass\/","title":{"rendered":"GLASS"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"FITT_Article_top\">\n<div class=\"dHdHP jLREf zXXje aGO eCClZ nTLv jLsYA gmuro TOSFd VmeZt sCkVm hkQai wGrlE MUuGM fciaN qQjt DhNVo Tgcqk IGLAf tWjkv \">\n<div class=\"PrismLeadContainer\">\n<div class=\"GpQCA vUYNV glxIO bmjsw KxZZC \">\n<div class=\"SplitLead PrismArticleLead Kiog bmjsw qLXqf HfASR WnNjf QUllD Vzwln Oqynf ltjWz la-DEb MrlBD TTngH WNDwH PFgXx KHfSH SUJE DKtDg ixak qHNrw pHRqk Mllfg MkFYc XVsI YxaoI TaAEi gTIDq cFUKH txLGj bnilD \" data-testid=\"prism-SplitLead\">\n<div class=\"tIfqR VZTD mLASH YOODG RONPx qWnSF StNUh wEyYM bywdO \">\n<div class=\"VZTD UeCOM jIRH oimqG DjbQm UwdmX Xmrlz ReShI KaJdY lqtkC ssImf HfYhe RTHNs DqtYD JZkow \" data-testid=\"prism-GridContainer\">\n<div class=\"Kiog kNVGM nvpSA qwdi bmjsw nTFI \" data-testid=\"prism-GridRow\">\n<div class=\"theme-e oBTii mrzah \" data-testid=\"prism-GridColumn\">\n<div class=\"NutQb eLoqD AEsTC bTijh vqrXY IsXFX aOdPl \" data-testid=\"prism-LeadContent\">\n<div class=\"awXxV \" data-testid=\"prism-articleLeadMeta\">\n<div class=\" \" data-testid=\"prism-badge-tag-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"IKUxI xFOBK YsVzB NuCDJ fMJDZ ZCNuU tZcZX JuzoE \">\n<div class=\"jVJih nAZp \" data-testid=\"prism-tags\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">A glass revolution is underway. Spoiler alert: it bends and bounces<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"kCTVx PPjDx pOKAh glxIO HfYhe vUYNV VGOqD nDkuk uCVfO eQSuB \" data-testid=\"prism-headline\">\n<p class=\"FRnbR Poyse uieav lqtkC glxIO HfYhe vUYNV kjxhK pUhmG hDCuW \"><span class=\"gtOSm FbbUW tUtYa vOCwz EQwFq yCufu eEak Qmvg nyTIa SRXVc vzLa jgBfc WXDas CiUCW kqbG zrdEG txGfn ygKVe BbezD UOtxr CVfpq xijV soGRS XgdC sEIlf daWqJ \" style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Humans have been making glass for 4,000 years. But now, scientists are developing techniques that will impact everything from medicine to the way we see the universe.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"pFYvw GpQCA pWDoc NAOo tRYWy vzGeY Zuecj ilnrB HZlx SHYeL \">\n<div class=\"KwyL lZur ymbLA qTfbe \">\n<div class=\"lZur TmzDJ bmjsw \" data-testid=\"prism-copyright-wrapper\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><picture data-testid=\"prism-picture\"><source srcset=\"https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=374&amp;h=281, https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=748&amp;h=562 2x\" media=\"(max-width: 374px)\" \/><source srcset=\"https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=413&amp;h=310, https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=826&amp;h=620 2x\" media=\"(min-width: 375px) and (max-width: 413px)\" \/><source srcset=\"https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=767&amp;h=575, https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=1534&amp;h=1150 2x\" media=\"(min-width: 414px) and (max-width: 767px)\" \/><source srcset=\"https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=1024&amp;h=768, https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=2048&amp;h=1536 2x\" media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px)\" \/><source srcset=\"https:\/\/i.natgeofe.com\/n\/6f2eeec2-1807-4146-a60f-0bb4fa7e8760\/MM9817_231004_03302.jpg?w=1260&am